<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In my case, I want to get into a view helper all messages from different namespaces (error, warning, notice, ok).
A method like this is very helpful to handle this situation.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
/**
 * getCurrentNamespaces() - get all used namespaces
 *
 * @return array
 */
public function getCurrentNamespaces()
{
    return array_keys(self::$_messages);
}
    
/**
 * getNamespaces() - get all used namespaces
 *
 * @return array
 */
public function getNamespaces()
{
    $namespaces = array();
    foreach (self::$_session as $key =&gt; $namespace) {
        $namespaces[] = $key;
    }
    return $namespaces;
}
</code></pre>

